    public class PrintPreview
extends android.support.v7.app.AppCompatActivity
    The intent of this class is to allow KitKat device users to preview the print out prior to sending the print job to the printer. This class is only used within the HP Print SDK (You should not create this activity by yourself). In the future, we may allow UI customization within this activity.
